- add_issue_comment: Add a comment to an existing issue
    Input Schema:
    {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "owner": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "repo": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "issue_number": {
          "type": "number"
        },
